Cambodia: Suryavarman II died, possibly in a military campaign against the Cham of Central Vietnam. Dharanindravarman II succeeded him.
China: Xizong was murdered in a coup by Wanyan Liang, who succeeded him as emperor of Jin.
Philippine: Gat Timamanukum become the Lakan of the Tondo Dynasty.
Russia: With assistance of chorniye klobuky Iziaslav kicked away Yuri from Kiev. After some time, with help of Volodimirko of Galych, Yuri took Kiev again.
